Class Manufacturer

  • java.lang.Object
    • Main_Logic.Manufacturer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    public class Manufacturer
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable, java.io.Serializable
    Represents a manufacturer that sells products. Implements Cloneable and Serializable interfaces. Overrides clone and toString methods.
